imdb.plot outline: Discover the journey of pregnancy and parenthood through this video series. Tara Nicodemo, host of Amazing Milestones meets with different members of the community, from doctors to expecting moms-to-be, to explore interesting topics pertaining a mother's prenatal experience and her child's developmental milestones and nutrition.
imdb.title: Enfamil Amazing Milestones
